Context - User is a manager and has selected a specific product within inventory and clicked produce

Primary Flow -
1 - System retrieves product information from the server
2 - System shows the product information to the user
3 - User inputs the quantity of the product to produce
4 - User selects produce button
5 - System validates that there are enough raw material to produce specified product 
5 - System updates raw material information and product information 
6 - System notifies the user about sucessful production
7 - System display the Product tabpage

Alternative flow(s)
CANCEL
a1-2 - user selects cancel
a2-3 - system displays product tab page

BAD CONNECTION
a2 - system can't connect to server
a3 - system informs user of failure and prompts to retry later
return to step 7

NOT ENOUGH RAW MATERIALS
?? - System informs user of invalid raw material amount
return to step 3